  "texts": [
    "• TF Encrypted for encrypted computation.",
    "These libraries could easily benefit from each other, for example, including differential privacy (TF Privacy) during the training of a model in a federated architecture (TF Federated).",
    "However, they are developed separately, so there are still no obvious integration points, as expected (TF-Federated-doc 2024).",
    "Federated supports differentially private aggregation as well, using adaptive clipping and Gaussian noise.",
    "Syft is OpenMined's open-source stack that provides secure and private Data Science in Python (OpenMined 2023b)."
  ]
